			 respectively, and by inserting after<cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Homeland Security Act of 2002/s:2008/ss:a/p:9">paragraph (9)</cato:entity-ref>the following:</text>
        <quoted-block id="H1E536413BEC441779B411002A52808C1" style="OLC">
          <paragraph id="H7923CBEE8991400DB85272FCA3477DA7">
            <enum>(10)</enum>
            <text>enhancing medical
				preparedness, medical surge capacity, and mass prophylaxis capabilities,
				including the development and maintenance of an initial pharmaceutical
